rooms.Name: Entrance into MMPR Area
rooms.Description:
This is your starting point into the Final area of Bigh's quest:  to face the
Power Ranger Zeo Zords.  There are No Dt's here.  This is where you can only
return and recall and the place where you receive your corpse.  The rest of this
zone will be made so that you cannot recall and cannot teleport so beware.

rooms.Name: One O'Clock
rooms.Description:
You find yourself standing on the face of a clock.  The time seems to slow.
There is a loud ticking sound pounds inside your chest as seconds slip away
from the hour.

rooms.Name: Twelve O'Clock Midnight
rooms.Description:
The time has come to put away the century old Father Time and bring in the
newborn Millenium.  Happy New Year!!

rooms.Name: New Years Day Quest Staging Area
rooms.Description:
This is the room where you get yer group together to enter into time.  If
(when) you die.. tell MotherTime "transme" and she will bring you back to
this room.  This is the only room that you can recall, relocate or quit from.
Once the quest begins, there will not be anyone else allowed to join.. unless
the group that is present votes to allow them to join.  If you leave early
for what ever reason you will not get "your share" of the quest points.

rooms.Name: Zeo Ranger Holding place
rooms.Description: This Area holds all the rangers (morphed and unmorphed) until the quest begins.

rooms.Name: At the top of the tower.
rooms.Description:
You stand at the top of the tower. There are windows to the north and south.
Through them you can see miles of forrest in both directions.

rooms.Name: Beneath the tower.
rooms.Description:
You stand beneath the wizards tower. You can hear loud booms, and the clanking
of metal far above you head.

rooms.Name: In the main hall of the castle.
rooms.Description:
You stand in the main hall of the ancient castle. The stone walls tower above
your head. You notice several blood stains on th floor.

rooms.Name: In a secret tunnel.
rooms.Description: You have found a secret passage leading under the ancient castle.

rooms.Name: In a secret tunnel.
rooms.Description: You have found a secret passage leading under the ancient castle.

rooms.Name: The moat.
rooms.Description:
This is a moat surrounding an ancient forbidden castle. Strange noises come
from the water. Perhaps this is not a safe place.

rooms.Name: The moat.

This is a moat surrounding an ancient forbidden castle. Strange noises come
from the water. Perhaps this is not a safe place.

rooms.Name: Among the sunflowers
rooms.Description:
You come upon an area of the field that is completely dominated by large
sunflowers.  Bunblebees and other insects dart about looking for the days
food supply, while small animals scurry about in the underbrush.

rooms.Name: Flowers in the field.
rooms.Description:
As you come upon this drastically different part of the field,
you notice a sweetness hovering in the air.  The birds and other
animals roaming throughout this flowery field seem to be engulfed
in a sort of jovial atmosphere.

ExtraDescs.Description:
The flowers here dance brilliantly and almost force you to
think of happier times.

rooms.Name: An open field.
rooms.Description:
A field stretches out before you and meets the sky at a great distance.  The
land here is quite flat and the underbrush is populated by various prairie
creatures.  You notice that someone has camped here recently as there are
signs of a campfire.

ExtraDescs.Description:
A circle of stones surrounds a blackened area where a
fire recently roared.
In the distance, the ground and sky meet at the horizon.

rooms.Name: In the field
rooms.Description:
The wind dies completely here and you are left with a feeling of peace and
tranquility.  Butterflies and bumblebees dance mystically in and about the
wide variety of plantlife growning in this field.

ExtraDescs.Description:
There is a wide variety of plants stretching out as far as you
can see, most of which are flowers.

rooms.Name: Before the spring
rooms.Description:
The overall beauty of the scenery surrounding you is nearly breathtaking.
Tall, ageless trees tower above you as the soft soothing sound of
gurgling water can be heard from the crystal clear pool of water.  
The sparkling water pool reflects your image vividly as you contemplate
taking a drink from it.

ExtraDescs.Description:
Huge, ageless trees that have withstanded the test of time
shade you from the heat of the day, and protect you from the cold
of the night.

rooms.Name: The edge of a field
rooms.Description:
The trail widens here into a pleasant grassy field that is covered with lush
green grass swaying gently in the breeze. You hear birds chirping and the
tranquil sound of water gugling in the near distance.

rooms.Name: End of the trail
rooms.Description:
The trail is gradually getting wider and apparently more widely used, as
the grass and weeds that grow within it are becoming more sparse.  In
the distance, you can see the dark outline of a cliff face looming
over the treetops.

rooms.Name: On a trail
rooms.Description:
The path widens here into something that more closely resembles a trail.
The breeze that meanders through the trees is refreshing, however it
cannot hide the evidence of recent travellers that have also journeyed
upon this trail.  The air surrounding you is crisp and clean.

rooms.Name: A path in the woods
rooms.Description:
You find yourself on a small dirt trail that leads off into towards a high
cliff.  The peaceful sounds of squirrels chittering and birds chirping is all
that can be heard.

rooms.Name: Floating in a portal
rooms.Description:
Welcome to the Pokemon Death Quest!  You have been transported to this room
in final preparations for this quest.  If (when) you die... you will be
brought back to this room and allowed to attempt to get your corpse.
